9. PHASE 2 COMPLETED SECURITY HARDENING & TRUST SEAL
---------------------------------------------------------
- Security Files Created:
  * `app/src/main/java/com/mpowernet/shesafe/security/KeyStoreManager.kt` (Passphrase generator & Keystore wrapper)
  * `app/src/main/java/com/mpowernet/shesafe/security/DatabaseIntegrityVerifier.kt` (SHA-256 boot integrity validator)
  * `app/src/main/java/com/mpowernet/shesafe/security/PlayIntegrityVerifier.kt` (Play Integrity & Local Signature checker)

- Security Features Integrated:
  * SQLCipher Database Encryption: Upgraded Room DB configuration in `AppDatabase.kt` to encrypt the local SQLite database using a 256-bit AES cryptographic passphrase generated dynamically and encrypted using Android KeyStore-backed AES/GCM keys.
  * Boot-Time Integrity Check: Evaluates database signature hash in `SheSafeApplication.kt`. Triggers high-risk warning screens if file tampering is detected. Automatically updates expected hash upon valid user consent database writes to avoid false positives.
  * Tapjacking Protection: Injected `filterTouchesWhenObscured = true` and `FLAG_SPLIT_TOUCH` on the overlay window layouts in `PermissionInterceptorService.kt` to prevent tap hijack redirection.
  * Personal Trust Seal: Added Settings selection in `MainActivity` (Sunflower 🌻, Heart ❤️, Star ⭐, etc.). Displays selected seal floating on top-right corner of consequence card overlays to allow visual identification of phishing popup layouts.
  * Signature Attestation: Checks local package signer against expected production certificate hash as fallback if Google Play Integrity services are unreachable.
